title: philipma1957
author: philipma1957
content: First question is does the a1166 psu work for the a1246 unit.I think my a1246 blew the psu I have an extra a1166 psu.here is the log for the a1246I am pretty sure the -273 mean dead psu

comments.author: BitMaxz
comments.body: If the PSU model is psu3300-03 then I think it should be compatible.About your logs ECHU and ECMM is pointing to your control board or connection problem that is why you get -273.If you have extra control board try to switch it or try to reflash your unit because bootby shows abnormal value.

comments.author: philipma1957

comments.body: Quote from: BitMaxz on January 05, 2023, 06:42:27 PMIf the PSU model is psu3300-03 then I think it should be compatible.About your logs ECHU and ECMM is pointing to your control board or connection problem that is why you get -273.If you have extra control board try to switch it or try to reflash your unit because bootby shows abnormal value.thank you. I only have 1 a1246 I do have the correct spare psu.I will try that.edit:I found Avalon buddy it reads psu is failed.I will drive to the mine over the week and replace it.

comments.author: Rodemi
comments.body: Avalon PSU3300-03, PSU3300-03 PLUS, PSU3300-03 PLUS 2 power supplies are compatible with AvalonMiner A1066, A1066Pro, A1166, A1166Pro and A1246, can be used universally.

comments.author: philipma1957
comments.body: Avalon buddy says dead psu.I have a 3300-03 psu new in stock.Maybe go to fix it on monday.
